{"id": 4954, "title": "Ticket #4954: Master ticket for submit file parser change and new macros", "description": "<blockquote>\nThere are a number of tests needed to validate things capable from  submit file syntax and parser changes. Include/if-else comes from using config parser.\nThe submit file changes allow script avoidance tools and the new macros provide additional tools at expansion time. For a quick overview see tickets <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4819\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4819'); return false;\" title='\"queue\" for multiple files'>#4819</a></span> and <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4944\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4944'); return false;\" title=\"New $macro expansion functions for submit\">#4944</a></span> .\n\n<p></p><ol>\n<li>Allow whole line substitution for output and queue in SimpleJob.pm <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4955\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4955'); return false;\" title=\"SimpleJob.pm cannot handle new submit sysntax and macros\">#4955</a></span></li></ol>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4955\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4955'); return false;\" title=\"SimpleJob.pm cannot handle new submit sysntax and macros\">#4955</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nSimpleJob.pm cannot handle new submit sysntax and macros</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<